article.headline: Thomas' 18 help Rhode Island defeat Fairfield 96-58
article.description: — Sebastian Thomas' 18 points helped Rhode Island defeat Fairfield 96-58 on Monday night.
article.linkText: Thomas' 18 help Rhode Island defeat Fairfield 96-58
article.story: KINGSTON, R.I. -- — Sebastian Thomas' 18 points helped Rhode Island defeat Fairfield 96-58 on Monday night. Thomas also had seven assists for the Rams. Jaden House scored 16 points while going 4 of 6 and 7 of 8 from the free-throw line. Tyonne Farrell had 14 points and shot 5 of 8 from the field and 3 of 3 from the free-throw line. Louis Bleechmore finished with 13 points for the Stags. Prophet Johnson added nine points and 11 rebounds for Fairfield. Noah Best also recorded nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
